  "id": "RAW_5118beb5",
  "title": "Claude 推出军师模式：最强模型 Opus 只做幕后大脑，实现智商飙升与成本优化",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&mid=2247513944&idx=1&sn=9b523e0dec1ef80779935f59bacc274f",
  "date": "2026-04-10 05:50:00",
